{"id":314015,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/【图说天朝】老无所依-圆梦中国/","date":"2013-09-18T08:16:00Z","modified":"2013-10-05T00:15:27Z","title":"【图说天朝】老无所依 圆梦中国","content":"<p>9月3日，贵州贵阳市，101岁高龄的四川老人谭小珍拾荒度日。老太太说“来贵州五十几年了，没有户口、没有收入。因为年迈找不到活路，领不到低保，只能到处捡拾泡沫。”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-314026\" alt=\"9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732-300x197.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/9ecf146bcf0b2a84f0844264f0733732-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>老人在菜市场捡泡沫废品。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-314027\" alt=\"e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3-300x194.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/e051139dfab976bc526138abb8b537d3-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>废旧塑料卖给回收垃圾的商家，每天能有几十块钱的收入。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/f8fee98cdecabee66d4918d005b2caa7.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-314028\" alt=\"f8fee98cdecabee66d4918d005b2caa7\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/f8fee98cdecabee66d4918d005b2caa7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/f8fee98cdecabee66d4918d005b2caa7.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/f8fee98cdecabee66d4918d005b2caa7-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p>老人背着泡沫箱在大街上穿行。注意左侧标语。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/8ad733b85384596e52a05e34be75d163.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-314029\" alt=\"8ad733b85384596e52a05e34be75d163\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/8ad733b85384596e52a05e34be75d163.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/8ad733b85384596e52a05e34be75d163.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/8ad733b85384596e52a05e34be75d163-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=2ea93c5b7b\" method=\"POST\"><a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a></p>\n</form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[14493,19194,19192,20925,11663]}